
OrangeHRM Selenium Automation Framework (Python + Pytest)

This project is a **modular web automation framework** using:

-  Python + Selenium
-  Page Object Model (POM) structure
-  `pytest` test runner
-  `pytest-html` for beautiful HTML reports

It automates the login and logout functionality of [OrangeHRM](https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/) and serves as a solid starting point for larger test automation projects.

---

##  Project Structure

WebScraping using selenium/
├── chromedriver.exe # Chrome driver executable
├── pages/ # Page Object Model classes
│ ├── login_page.py # LoginPage class (enter username/password, click login)
│ └── homepage.py # Homepage class (logout actions)
├── tests/
│ └── test_login.py # Test class using pytest

Run with pytest:
"pytest tests/test_login.py --html=reports/test_report.html --self-contained-html" for reports
